model.InexistentDatabaseEntityException

java.io.Serializable
public class InexistentDatabaseEntityException
extends java.lang.Exception
Exception used when a savable object's id is accessed. Remark that savable objects should be used only befroe saving them in the database. Thus, they don't have an id.
